{
  "stem": "17543.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 212.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was living on a main-- it was a flat on a main road, which is right in the center of Budapest.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there was a red store, which does the printing for one of these Hungarian newspapers.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And people was climbing up and pulling down the ropes and the trumps, which goes on the street-- they were smashed windows and barricades was on the-- on the railway lines.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know, you couldn't go A to B.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And everything was-- all windows-- this is main road, I'm talking about.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The windows were smashed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You couldn't get any food.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was really frightening.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "A radio station was on, constantly was saying-- constantly with music, so you couldn't tell what's going on.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Nobody knew what's happening.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So I don't know even today why it was starting, who done it, and what was happening.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So it was [INAUDIBLE] for some really lengthy time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I don't know how long-- some weeks.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It was going on that when friends decided to go to the border town, which one near to Austria, because heard from other paper down there.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we had some kind of transfer to get to the Austrian border, last town in Hungary.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And everybody throwed away their identity card and walked through on the no man's land, which I'm told was mines on it.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Luckily, we didn't step on any of them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And on the other side in Austria was waiting the Red Cross-- again [LAUGHS] the Red Cross.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they had [SOBBING] [INAUDIBLE] never go back to Hungary ever, because what they'd done to let us-- they-- they offer us to the Germans, the Hungarian government then-- government.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They really offer to help to take us out.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
